lass=\"red\">&ldquo;需要由四國表露對華強硬姿態。同時讓對於牽制中國態度謹慎的印度留在框架內很重要。&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n▽隱患<br />\n<br />\n  日美澳印的立場顯然存在差異。澳大利亞加強對華批判，<span class=\"red\">總理莫里森將四國框架表述成&ldquo;為了地區和平與穩定依靠的繩索&rdquo;。印度重視&ldquo;戰略上的自立&rdquo;</span>。日美澳構想通過向力爭擴大疫苗生產的印度提供資金合作來彰顯共同步調，但無法預料在對華策略上將步調統一到何種程度。日本在今後的磋商中無法掌握主導權，在美印拉鋸之下被埋沒的憂慮也揮之不去。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2021/03/8a25a3750603--.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2F8a25a3750603--.html&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=50acc237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2021/03/8a25a3750603--.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"simon哥忘記提提你 連登這邊很討厭拜登 一直不相信他除了美言之外能拿出甚麼實際行動"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"台灣大多數人也是支持川普<br />\n但是面對未來，現在與拜登政府必須合作<br />\n否則怎麼抗共"},{"pid":"a3fee2cbbcd54bf110973ddc598efa761bb48ec0","tid":2444711,"uid":203305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwoJZV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwoJZV1.jpg&h=58c760d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國法院暫停左小米禁令<br />\n硬邊撚度硬"},{"pid":"9aaa9d9c31a17af629468a28e950756fe0bea021","tid":2444711,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"84bf2c308fc31212505af4dfad7b68a9bc063c2c","tid":2444711,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"221cafee4647a08fa7cadfac7cd292dd66ec374a","tid":2444711,"uid":244612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a33804f3504b88461e0c152b915f97297b909076","tid":2444711,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">聚焦：日本欲以四國合作應對中國 與美印存溫差</span></strong><br />\n共同社 共同社, 全球縱橫, 日本政治 15 小時前 - 22:53<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.kyodonews.net/chinese/public/images/posts/568db7d4c80a896f2642fbbb95071